ignore / chatignore           Stops listening out for incoming calls
 
   Format:
      ;ignore                 Ignores incoming calls
 
   Notes:
      The Chat task is used to chat with other players directly via telnet.
         Calls can be placed (or accepted) with any user whose MUD client uses
         the zChat or MudMaster protocols.
      Use ';chatlisten' to resume listening out for incoming calls.
 
   User commands:
      ignore / chatignore
